nllb_translation: It is a long-known white-lipped parchment document about the Deeney, though no one knows who wrote it. The Deeney is 29.3 inches by 24.6 inches, rolled up for storage.

nllb_translation: A civilization is a monotonic culture in which a society coexists and is shared by a substantially large group of people who work together.
gold_translation: A civilization is a singular culture shared by a significant large group of people who live and work co-operatively, a society.
